India's largest read youth magazine, Pratiyogita Darpan, has over 4.9 million readers. The Indian Readership Survey (IRS) ranked Pratiyogita Darpan as India's top 2nd magazine among all magazines published in India and ranked it as the No. 1 career and competition magazine. The magazine is an essential guide to the youth for their career and competition examinations. The magazine offers comprehensive reading material for aspirants of examinations like Union & State Civil Services, SSC, UGC/NET, Bank, MBA, etc.
